 P2y.jp  https://p2y.jp 2023 年 9 月 27 日星期三 16:23:01 +0000贾每小时1 https://wordpress.org/?v=6.2.2 https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/cropped-logo_2023_150x150-32x32.png P2y.jp https://p2y.jp 32 32 166157578
时雨《星圣！！萝莉神安魂曲☆》17天点击量突破1000万，创VTuber歌曲MV史上最快https://p2y.jp/shigure-ui-shukusei-loligami-requiem-achieved-10-million-views-in-17-days-the-fastest-in-vtuber-music-video-history/ https://p2y.jp/shigure-ui-shukusei-loligami-requiem-achieved-10-million-views-in-17-days-the-fastest-in-vtuber-music-video-history/#respondp2y_admin Wed, 27 Sep 2023 15:36:36 +0000 VTuberバーチャル音楽TwitterYouTubeYouTuberしぐれういバーチャルYouTuber個人勢 https://p2y.jp/?p=102163 <p>截至2023年9月27日（令和4），VTuber Shigureui（无隶属）9月10日发行的原创歌曲MV《Sekusei!! Loli God Requiem☆》的播放次数，与VTuber Talen相比[…]</p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/shigure-ui-shukusei-loligami-requiem-achieved-10-million-views-in-17-days-the-fastest-in-vtuber-music-video-history/">时雨伊的帖子《Seishei!! Loli God Requiem☆》17天内点击量突破1000万，VTuber歌曲MV史上最快​​首次</a>出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a> 。; <p></p><p>截至2023年9月27日（令和4），VTuber <strong>Shigureui</strong> （独立）表示，9月10日发布的原曲MV《 <strong>Sekusei!! Loli God Requiem☆</strong> 》的播放次数高于VTuber艺人的歌曲已确认，该音乐视频于17日已突破1000万次观看次数，这是音乐视频历史上最快的时间。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img data-attachment-id="102185" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/shigure-ui-shukusei-loligami-requiem-achieved-10-million-views-in-17-days-the-fastest-in-vtuber-music-video-history/shigure_ui_shukusei_loligami_requiem_achieved_10_million_views_in_17_days_the_fastest_in_vtuber_music_video_history/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/shigure_ui_shukusei_loligami_requiem_achieved_10_million_views_in_17_days_the_fastest_in_vtuber_music_video_history.jpg" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="shigure_ui_shukusei_loligami_requiem_achieved_10_million_views_in_17_days_the_fastest_in_vtuber_music_video_history" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/shigure_ui_shukusei_loligami_requiem_achieved_10_million_views_in_17_days_the_fastest_in_vtuber_music_video_history.jpg" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/shigure_ui_shukusei_loligami_requiem_achieved_10_million_views_in_17_days_the_fastest_in_vtuber_music_video_history.jpg" decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/shigure_ui_shukusei_loligami_requiem_achieved_10_million_views_in_17_days_the_fastest_in_vtuber_music_video_history.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-102185"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：YouTube<br> © 时雨伊</figcaption></figure><p>《Sekusei!! Loli God Requiem☆》是时雨衣于2022年5月25日发行的专辑《Mada Ame wa Yamanai》（令和4）中收录的歌曲。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="[原创歌曲] Shusei!! Loli God Requiem ☆ / Shigureui（9岁）" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ci_zad39Uhw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="时雨依第一张完整专辑《Still Rain Don&#39;t Stop》XFD" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/7AiY8-OLYIs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><div class="yjmze651536915b125" ><script async src="https://pagead2