</style><p>虽然菲利安被曝患有ADHD（注意力缺陷多动症），但他精通健康和生物方面的知识，他在节目中也展现了这种能力。</p><p> 7 月 13 日，他成为第三位在其官方 YouTube 频道上拥有 200 万订阅者的活跃英语人才。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="2,000,000！！" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qWC83b3L6Vs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="fed61zE01q"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/filian-becomes-the-3rd-active-english-speaking-vtuber-in-history-to-reach-2-million-youtube-subscribers/">filian 成为第三个拥有 200 万订阅者的英语 VTuber。</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“filian 成为第三位拥有 200 万订阅者的英语 VTuber” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/filian-becomes-the-3rd-active-english-speaking-vtuber-in-history-to-reach-2-million-youtube-subscribers/embed/#?secret=Zh3feLQdw2#?secret=fed61zE01q" data-secret="fed61zE01q" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="A4yWEdr68d"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/houshou-marine-becomes-the-first-vtuber-in-japan-to-have-700-million-total-views-of-videos-on-her-official-youtube-channel/">日本VTuber中Hosho Marine YouTube官方频道视频观看次数首次突破7亿次</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VTuber 的 Hosho Marine YouTube 官方频道视频观看次数在日本首次突破 7 亿” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/houshou-m